The chunk of code needs to be inserted after all message types have been defined and registered. It maps each message type name to its descriptor and registers the file descriptor with the symbol database.

```python
# After defining and registering all message types...

DESCRIPTOR.message_ypes_by_name['MultiAbiTargeting'] = _MULTIABITARGETING
DESCRIPTOR.message_ypes_by_name['ScreenDensityTargeting'] = _SCREENDENSITYTARGETING
DESCRIPTOR.message_ypes_by_name['LanguageTargeting'] = _LANGUAGETARGETING
DESCRIPTOR.message_ypes_by_name['SdkVersionTargeting'] = _SDKVERSIONTARGETING
DESCRIPTOR.message_ypes_by_name['TextureCompressionFormatTargeting'] = _TEXTURECOMPRESSIONFORMATTARGETING
DESCRIPTOR.message_ypes_by_name['SanitizerTargeting'] = _SANITIZERTARGETING
DESCRIPTOR.message_ypes_by_name['DeviceFeatureTargeting'] = _DEVICEFEATURETARGETING
DESCRIPTOR.message_ypes_by_name['DeviceTierTargeting'] = _DEVICETIERTARGETING
DESCRIPTOR.message_ypes_by_name['DeviceGroupModuleTargeting'] = _DEVICEGROUPMODULETARGETING
_ sym_db.RegisterFileDescriptor(DESCRIPTOR)
```
